cs.CL, cs.IR, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CY 

This paper deals with natural language processing and information extraction in the context of clinical trials. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CL (Computation and Language). The paper also involves machine learning techniques, which could fall under cs.IR (Information Retrieval) or cs.LG (Machine Learning). Additionally, the use of a knowledge base and context information suggests a possible fit with cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.CY (Computers and Society).
